        "source_sentence": "一商人至衖亭湖祭神。",
        "translation": "A merchant went to Śubhaketu to worship a god.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b13_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夜夢神云。",
        "translation": "In the night, he dreamed the god said.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b13_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸君以所贈物與嚴法華為書經用也。",
        "translation": "'You've given us this gift, and we'll use it to write sūtras on the Dharma Flower of Adamantine.'",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b14_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其他感應甚眾。",
        "translation": "There were many other blessings.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b14_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "恭遂以書經終。",
        "translation": "Kō then ended up writing sūtras.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b15_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大業末。",
        "translation": "At the end of his great career, his descendants continued to hand down his work.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b15_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "子孫猶傳其業。",
        "translation": "His descendants still passed on his work.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b15_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "群盜相約不入其里。",
        "translation": "A group of thieves agreed not to enter his village.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b15_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "里人賴之。",
        "translation": "The people of the village relied on him.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b16_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "同時益州新繁有荀生者。",
        "translation": "At the same time, there was a man named Xun Sheng from Xinfan in Yizhou.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b16_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "居縣西三十里許曰王李村。",
        "translation": "He lived 30 miles west of the county in a village called Wang Li.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b16_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "工書。",
        "translation": "He was a great calligrapher.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b17_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然自重不肯為人書。",
        "translation": "However, he respected himself and wouldn't write for others.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b17_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人雖辱毆之。",
        "translation": "Although people insulted him, he was assaulted.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b18_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不顧也。",
        "translation": "He didn't care.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b18_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一日把筆走前村。",
        "translation": "One day, he put his writing brush in his hand and walked to the front village.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b18_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "向空中四面書般若經。",
        "translation": "He wrote the Prajñāpāramitā Sutra on all four sides of the sky.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b18_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "數日而畢曰。",
        "translation": "After a few days, he finished it, saying.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b19_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "好令諸天讀之。",
        "translation": "\"I want the gods to read it.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b19_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人初不覺其異。",
        "translation": "At first, people didn't think it was different.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b19_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其後大雷雨。",
        "translation": "Later, there was a huge thunderstorm.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b20_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "牧牛小兒住其地中可丈許。",
        "translation": "A small cowherd boy lives on the ground up to a few feet inside it.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b20_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雨不能濕。",
        "translation": "It couldn't get wet in the rain.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b20_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自後遇雨牧兒輙避雨其處。",
        "translation": "From then on, when it rained, the herd boys would often take refuge in that place.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b21_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "武德中有異僧語村人曰。",
        "translation": "In the midst of Wude, a different monk told the villagers.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b21_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此地空中有般若經。",
        "translation": "\"There's a Prajñāpāramitā sūtra in the sky above this place.",
        "source": "X88n1646_004:0190b22_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸天於上設葢覆之。",
